Hub version 04.00.043
=====================

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES
------------

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI 						3.11
  Carp 						1.01.
  Compress::Zlib 	1.33.
  Cwd 						2.12.
  Exporter 				5.57.
  File::Copy 			2.07.
  IO::File 				1.10.
  Time::HiRes 		1.55.

For :webapp functions

	Bundle::Apache2
	Image::Size
  Digest::SHA1 (or Crypt::DSA)

